00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:27,940
He loves you more than anyone in this world,

375
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,730
no matter what.

376
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:36,530
I won't ask you

377
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:40,730
