00:30:25,540 --> 00:30:27,580
♪I can see♪

454
00:30:29,340 --> 00:30:31,380
♪Right through you...♪

455
00:30:33,750 --> 00:30:34,490
That's right.

456
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:37,570
He conspired with Jiang Xiang to kill my mother.

