505
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:55,290
I can't afford

506
00:32:55,750 --> 00:32:56,940
to alert my enemy.

507
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,770
You want me to figure out

508
00:33:00,590 --> 00:33:02,010
