530
00:34:11,590 --> 00:34:12,610
Blood for blood.

531
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:16,690
This rule has remained unchanged for thousands of years.

532
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:27,340
I will try to help you.

533
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:31,170
