00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:22,980
that much of the money embezzled by Zhuang Zhifu

569
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:25,530
has ended up in Cao Jingxian's pocket.

570
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,260
That's expected.

571
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:30,490
Besides, he's surrounded by layers of security.

572
00:36:31,150 --> 00:36:32,180
He's either in the palace

573
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:34,610
or at his private residence in the Capital.

574
00:36:35,030 --> 00:36:38,340
It's almost impossible to reach him.

575
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:41,860
However,

576
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:44,860
there will be an opportunity in two months.

577
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,300
What are you referring to?

578
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:50,170
The ground polo competition held by the imperial court

579
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:52,460
to strengthen the fitness of men in the Great Yong.

580
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:55,690
It's quite popular among the noble families.

581
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:58,900
The Seal-Holding Eunuch Director

582
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:00,490
brings rewards to the champion

583
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:02,340
on behalf of His Majesty every year.

584
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:05,570
That will be your chance to meet Cao Jingxian.

585
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:09,650
The opportunity comes at just the right time.

586
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:42,650
Aren't you tired of practicing Wuji Fist over and over again

587
00:37:43,070 --> 00:37:43,860
all day long?

588
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:44,490
Try something else.

589
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:46,490
You are the disciple and he is the master.

590
00:37:47,190 --> 00:37:48,490
And you're slacking off here?

591
00:37:49,490 --> 00:37:50,260
Zhinu.

592
00:37:50,710 --> 00:37:51,460
What brings you here?

593
00:37:51,670 --> 00:37:52,780
What did I tell you?

594
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:54,570
Call me Zang Hai from now on.

595
00:37:59,070 --> 00:38:01,490
Isn't this Young Master Zhuang?

596
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:03,010
You recognize me?

597
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:05,010
Sir.

598
00:38:05,670 --> 00:38:06,860
Why did you ask me out

599
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:08,260
and bring me here?

600
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,740
You are going to practice martial arts here.

601
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:15,010
Since you want to regain your father's favor,

602
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:17,490
then you can't follow your brother's path.

603
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,090
We have to find another way.

604
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:20,980
We must convince your father

605
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,490
that you have the potential

606
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:23,980
to inherit his mantle.

607
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:25,170
Shilei.

608
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:27,650
See if he is cut out to be a martial artist.

609
00:38:28,030 --> 00:38:28,460
Alright.

610
00:38:33,150 --> 00:38:34,010
Are you crazy?

611
00:38:34,440 --> 00:38:36,130
His father is the Marquis of Pingjin.

612
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:38,570
What if he figures out who you are?

613
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:39,980
He already knows.

614
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:41,280
Then...

615
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:43,260
Of course, he also knows who you are.

616
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,690
Then why is he still alive?

617
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:47,650
Rest assured.

618
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,740
He has allied with me.

619
00:38:50,480 --> 00:38:52,460
He will be practicing martial arts here.

620
00:38:53,710 --> 00:38:55,690
Make sure Shilei teaches him well.

621
00:38:57,590 --> 00:38:58,090
Guanfeng.

622
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,860
He is more gifted than you.

623
00:39:00,150 --> 00:39:01,490
I see potential in him.

624
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:02,530
Shut up.

625
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:07,600
He idles around and does nothing all day long.

626
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:08,860
Will he make it?

627
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,460
It's time to show me what you've got.

628
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:14,130
I'm entrusting him to you two.

629
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:17,300
You have two months to make him a martial artist.

630
00:39:18,510 --> 00:39:19,010
Sir.

631
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:21,260
Can we go somewhere else?

632
00:39:21,550 --> 00:39:23,250
This place is run down.

633
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:24,570
I don't even see a decent table.

634
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:26,940
Besides, where do I sleep?

635
00:39:27,550 --> 00:39:28,130
So...

636
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:33,380
I'll stop.

637
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:35,340
Sir.

638
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:36,570
It's fine here.

639
00:39:38,030 --> 00:39:38,780
From now on,

640
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:41,260
learn martial arts from these two masters.

641
00:39:43,190 --> 00:39:44,820
Remember. You promised

642
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,380
to do whatever I say.

643
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:50,570
This is your first step toward a transformation.

644
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:52,740
Of course, I'll be busy, too.

645
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,980
I have to work on your reputation in the Capital.

646
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:03,860
Fists facing down.

647
00:40:07,410 --> 00:40:09,770
Can you squat properly or not?

648
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:10,490
Yes, I can.

649
00:40:11,230 --> 00:40:12,230
Look at me.

650
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:15,940
This is a proper horse stance.

651
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:17,530
I see.

652
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:23,980
Can I have a bite?

653
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:25,260
Don't slack off.

654
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,400
I'm thirsty and hungry.

655
00:40:27,710 --> 00:40:28,860
Let me have a bite, please.

656
00:40:29,710 --> 00:40:30,820
Keep practicing and we'll see.

657
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,570
Turn around. Squat.

658
00:40:39,500 --> 00:40:40,630
[Cao's Mansion]

659
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:41,130
Mr. Lu,

660
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:44,260
please let me see Mr. Cao for a second.

661
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,050
I will be reassured as long as

662
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:47,300
everything is alright.

663
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:49,010
Why do you want to

664
00:40:49,550 --> 00:40:50,420
see our Lord, Mr. Chu?

665
00:40:56,510 --> 00:40:57,820
I observed the celestial signs.

666
00:40:58,400 --> 00:40:59,780
The Mandate Star shone brightly.

667
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,300
I read the signs.

668
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:04,010
Mr. Cao serves as His Majesty's closest court official.

669
00:41:04,230 --> 00:41:05,490
So he is the Mandate Star.

670
00:41:06,670 --> 00:41:08,050
Great news is to be expected.

671
00:41:08,230 --> 00:41:10,300
- I... - Since you don't have something to say,

672
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:12,020
please go back, Mr. Chu.

673
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:20,690
I was humiliated by others.

674
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:22,510
Please do me justice.

675
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:23,620
Mr. Chu.

676
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:26,050
You are the Imperial Astronomer,

677
00:41:26,510 --> 00:41:27,490
a fifth-rank official.

678
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,570
Who dares to humiliate you?

679
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,820
I feel embarrassed.

680
00:41:32,960 --> 00:41:35,460
I am humiliated by the aide Zang Hai of the Marquis of Pingjin.

681
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:38,050
This person is insidious and vicious.

682
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:40,260
And he has become the top aide to the Marquis.

683
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,090
I have offended him.

684
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:43,130
I'm afraid that he is going to target me.

685
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:45,130
I seek your protection.

686
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:49,210
Aren't you backed by the Marquis?

687
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:51,130
What brings you to the Surveillance Office?

688
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:53,260
Mr. Lu, please don't say that.

689
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:54,940
I don't work for anyone.

690
00:41:55,510 --> 00:41:58,170
I only serve the imperial court and His Majesty.

691
00:42:01,920 --> 00:42:04,210
If Mr. Cao needs me to do anything one day,

692
00:42:04,360 --> 00:42:06,260
I will devote myself to it entirely

693
00:42:06,260 --> 00:42:07,340
until the last breath.

694
00:42:11,710 --> 00:42:12,300
I see.

695
00:42:12,920 --> 00:42:13,980
Mr. Chu, please go back.

696
00:42:21,280 --> 00:42:29,260
♪The Bian River flows♪

697
00:42:29,360 --> 00:42:34,210
♪The Si River flows♪

698
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:41,690
♪Through Guazhou's old ferry it goes♪

699
00:42:41,840 --> 00:42:49,690
♪Where Southern hills stand dotted in woe...♪

700
00:42:50,160 --> 00:42:51,900
Not even worth a second look.

701
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:52,780
Understood.

702
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:58,940
♪Eternal sorrow♪

703
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:26,980
♪Conceal the ambition in my eyes♪

704
00:43:29,500 --> 00:43:36,140
♪In my palm, I hold a dangerous desire♪

705
00:43:36,700 --> 00:43:39,460
♪Turbulent waves hidden in my sleeves♪

706
00:43:40,060 --> 00:43:42,780
♪Silent thunder echoes around♪

707
00:43:43,060 --> 00:43:45,020
♪However cunning you are♪

708
00:43:45,500 --> 00:43:47,580
♪I can see♪

709
00:43:49,300 --> 00:43:51,420
♪Right through you♪

710
00:43:57,780 --> 00:44:04,820
♪Schemes are my armor♪

711
00:44:04,980 --> 00:44:10,420
♪Overt plans are my weapons♪

712
00:44:11,980 --> 00:44:14,700
♪With restrained fury♪

713
00:44:15,380 --> 00:44:18,060
♪I purge the world's corruption♪

714
00:44:18,260 --> 00:44:20,300
♪The night is not dark♪

715
00:44:20,780 --> 00:44:22,860
♪Because♪

716
00:44:23,980 --> 00:44:29,460
♪My heart burns bright♪

717
00:44:32,260 --> 00:44:35,540
♪I control the shifting clouds♪

718
00:44:35,740 --> 00:44:38,300
♪I command the falling rain♪

719
00:44:38,460 --> 00:44:40,820
♪The compass of the human soul is unpredictable♪

720
00:44:40,940 --> 00:44:45,740
♪There will always be ups and downs♪

721
00:44:46,220 --> 00:44:49,540
♪I hold the power of life and death♪

722
00:44:49,740 --> 00:44:52,300
♪I grant and I take away♪

723
00:44:52,460 --> 00:44:55,980
♪When faith burns like the scorching sun♪

724
00:44:56,020 --> 00:44:59,500
♪I will sing aloud with you♪

725
00:44:59,620 --> 00:45:02,860
♪I am the sowing season♪

726
00:45:02,980 --> 00:45:06,260
♪I am the autumn harvest♪

727
00:45:06,500 --> 00:45:08,660
♪I am the world♪

728
00:45:08,860 --> 00:45:12,420
♪I am the people♪

729
00:45:13,620 --> 00:45:16,700
♪And you are also me♪
